# MA Crossover Strategy (Golden Cross / Death Cross)
### Algorithmic Trading Research | EUR/USD Forex | Python

A systematic trend-following strategy using **MA50/MA200 crossover** (Golden Cross & Death Cross) on EUR/USD daily data. Backtested over 3 years to evaluate performance on Forex markets.

---

## 📌 Strategy Logic

| Component | Parameter |
|---|---|
| Asset | EUR/USD (`EURUSD=X`) |
| Timeframe | Daily (1D) |
| Data Period | Jan 2022 — Jan 2025 |
| Fast MA | 50-day |
| Slow MA | 200-day |

**Golden Cross → BUY:** MA50 crosses above MA200 — signals start of uptrend

**Death Cross → SELL:** MA50 crosses below MA200 — signals start of downtrend

